data.title: Spain Real GDP YoY Quarterly Insights: National Accounts
data.meta_description: In depth view into Spain Real GDP YoY including historical data from 1996 to 2024, charts and stats.
data.text:
Spain Real GDP YoY is at 2.90%, compared to 2.60% last quarter and 2.00% last year. This is higher than the long term average of 2.03%.
